Description: SSH SOCKS proxy system tray application
 SSH Proxy Tray is a Qt5-based system tray application for managing
 SSH SOCKS proxy connections. It provides an easy-to-use interface
 for enabling/disabling SSH proxy tunnels and configuring them as
 system proxy or local-only proxy.
 .
 Features:
  - System tray integration
  - Enable/disable SSH SOCKS proxy
  - System proxy or local-only mode
  - Auto-connect on startup
  - Autostart support
  - Settings dialog for configuration
  - Real-time proxy status monitoring
